statements: SELECT * FROM network_performance_data;
SELECT data_id, timestamp, signal_strength FROM network_performance_data;
SELECT * FROM network_performance_data WHERE cell_id = 1;
SELECT data_id, timestamp, cell_id, signal_strength FROM network_performance_data WHERE signal_strength > 50;
SELECT MAX(latency) FROM network_performance_data;
SELECT * FROM network_performance_data WHERE latency > 50 ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT cell_id, AVG(signal_strength) AS avg_signal FROM network_performance_data GROUP BY cell_id HAVING AVG(signal_strength) > 80;
SELECT * FROM network_performance_data WHERE signal_strength BETWEEN 70 AND 90 ORDER BY cell_id ASC, timestamp DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT cell_id, MAX(latency) AS max_latency FROM network_performance_data GROUP BY cell_id ORDER BY max_latency DESC LIMIT 3;
SELECT MAX(signal_strength) AS max_signal_strength, MIN(latency) AS min_latency FROM network_performance_data;
SELECT * FROM 5g_network_performance_data WHERE network_type = '5G' ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT id, download_speed, upload_speed FROM 5g_network_performance_data WHERE download_speed > 100 ORDER BY id;
SELECT id, timestamp, performance_score FROM 5g_optimization_data WHERE cell_id = 12345;
SELECT * FROM 5g_network_performance_data WHERE timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31';
SELECT network_type, COUNT(id) AS total_records FROM 5g_network_performance_data GROUP BY network_type ORDER BY total_records DESC;
SELECT * FROM 5g_network_performance_data WHERE network_type = '5G' ORDER BY timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT id, download_speed, upload_speed FROM 5g_network_performance_data WHERE download_speed > 100 ORDER BY download_speed ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT cell_id, optimization_strategy, performance_score FROM 5g_optimization_data WHERE performance_score > 0.8 ORDER BY cell_id LIMIT 3;
